{"inkVersion":21,"root":[["\n",{"->":"storm_intro"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"storm_intro":[["#","^music_Rain","/#","#","^sfx_Lightning1","/#","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^The sea cried that night. Winds howled, waves like blades, cutting into the ship.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^My stars - gone and with them my hope.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Everything felt wrong.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^But I didn’t move, I just stood there drenched, clinging to pride or stubbornness","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^… I don’t even know.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Then came the first scream. ","#","^sfx_Scream-85294","/#","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Gone, pulled into the sea, another name lost to the ocean.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^This wasn’t the sea that I knew.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^No, tonight it’s a deathbed.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^The ship jerked, I hit the deck - hard.","\n","#","^sfx_Lightning2","/#","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^The stinging of rain, chaos, even more screams.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^How did I react again?","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Oh yes...","\n",["ev",{"^->":"storm_intro.0.129.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^Regain composure ",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"storm_intro.0.130.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^Stumble and fall ",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"storm_intro.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.129.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"regain_composure"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"storm_intro.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.130.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"stumble_fall"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"regain_composure":["#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I forced myself up, I tried my damndest to steady myself against the ship's sway. I grabbed my harpoon and aimed through the storm.","\n",{"->":"kraken_attack"},{"#f":1}],"stumble_fall":["#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I fell, my legs gave out again and again, my hands slipping on the soaked terrain. I reached around me for anything and found my harpoon. I was shaking, but alive.","\n",{"->":"kraken_attack"},{"#f":1}],"kraken_attack":[["#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Another tentacle. But this one was bigger, meaner. Not squid like, no...","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^this was different - violent, malevolent.","\n","#","^sfx_Lightning1","/#","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I gripped my compass, knuckles going white.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Luck never favoured me. No, I fought for everything I had. Every scar, every coin, every bit of respect.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^And I solemnly swear to the heavenly beings cursing me that I will not go down with this ship.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^But thinking, idling - costs everything.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I hear another scream, another crewmate gone. In the blink of an eye. ","#","^sfx_Scream-85294","/#","\n","#","^sfx_Lightning2","/#","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","#","^sfx_Walking-on-a-wet-surface-41742","/#","^I ran to the wheel, my boots slipping against the wet planks but I held on.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I tried to steer, to guide my beauty out of this nightmare but neither the Kraken nor the sea had any intention of letting me go.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","#","^sfx_Thunder-307513","/#","^Lightning again. A tentacle slamming down - it’s about to hit me.","\n","^I…","\n",["ev",{"^->":"kraken_attack.0.107.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^Make the shot",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"kraken_attack.0.108.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^Miss",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"kraken_attack.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.107.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"make_shot"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"kraken_attack.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.108.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":"miss_shot"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"make_shot":["#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","#","^sfx_Arrow-hitting-target-83810","/#","^I lifted my harpoon. I remembered all my training. Deep breath, I fired. Success - dead center.","\n",{"->":"aftermath"},{"#f":1}],"miss_shot":["#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","#","^sfx_Arrow-hitting-target-83810","/#","^My aim was off, I grazed it but not enough.","\n",{"->":"aftermath"},{"#f":1}],"aftermath":["#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^The damage was done, I saved myself but the wheel was gone - splintered.  ","#","^sfx_Log-split-88986","/#","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^We were stuck.","\n","#","^sfx_Lightning2","/#","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^There were only two of us and one thing left to try.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I released the ballast.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^The ship tilted violently. I was thrown overboard.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^But so was she - my last crewmate.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Falling towards the beast.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I tried reaching out, I tried saving her.","\n","#","^sfx_Lightning1","/#","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I couldn’t save her.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I lost her.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^My strength, my crew, my ship, my compass.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^All of it was gone.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^I hit the ocean.","\n","#","^Speaker:","ev",{"VAR?":"Name"},"out","/ev","/#","^Everything went dark as I sank into the abyss.","\n","#","^sfx_stop","/#","#","^music_stop","/#","#","^sfxstop","/#","#","^musicstop","/#","end",{"#f":1}],"global decl":["ev",0,{"VAR=":"Pearl_Affection"},0,{"VAR=":"Shad_Affection"},0,{"VAR=":"Rory_Affection"},0,{"VAR=":"Ravynn_Affection"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"Name"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"PronounHe"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"PronounHim"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"PronounHisApple"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"PronounHis"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"rory_exit_type"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"shad_exit_type"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"pearl_exit_type"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"ravynn_exit_type"},false,{"VAR=":"roryTrueName"},"/ev","end",null],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}